# For local development only (npx wrangler dev).
# Copy to .dev.vars and fill in. .dev.vars is gitignored.
#
# Only ONE of these needs a value: whichever provider LLM_PROVIDER in
# wrangler.toml is currently set to. Right now that is "gemini", so
# GEMINI_API_KEY is the one that matters — CEREBRAS_API_KEY is only
# needed if you switch LLM_PROVIDER back to "cerebras". Setting the
# wrong one is the most common reason the Ask box stops writing an
# answer (it still shows matched items either way).
#
# In production set it in the dashboard, or:
#   npx wrangler secret put GEMINI_API_KEY
#   npx wrangler secret put CEREBRAS_API_KEY
GEMINI_API_KEY=
CEREBRAS_API_KEY=
